OL,3,CThe 100-year-old petition inspiring
OL,4,Cthis year's Urdd Peace Message
OL,6,FThis year's Peace and Goodwill Message
OL,7,Ffrom the Urdd has been inspired by a
OL,8,Fpetition from 100 years ago.
OL,10,FThe Welsh Women's Peace Petition of
OL,11,F1923-1924 was signed by 400,000 women
OL,12,Facross Wales and is said to be seven
OL,13,Fmiles in length.
OL,15,FIn this year's message, the children
OL,16,Fstate "the challenge of our century's
OL,17,Fnext chapter" is the continuing need
OL,18,Fto advocate for peace and putting an
OL,19,Fend to atrocities, wars and violence.
