OL,3,CThe 100-year-old petition inspiring
OL,4,Cthis year's Urdd Peace Message
OL,6,FThe Urdd has spread its Peace and
OL,7,FGoodwill Message every year since 1922
OL,8,Fwith the young people of Wales
OL,9,Fthrowing a spotlight on themes that
OL,10,Fare important to them while sharing a
OL,11,Fmessage of peace with the world.
OL,13,FShared every year in May, it was
OL,14,Finitially spread through Morse code
OL,15,Fbefore moving onto an audio format
OL,16,Fthrough radio broadcasts and now is
OL,17,Fposted to social media.
