OL,3,CThe 100-year-old petition inspiring
OL,4,Cthis year's Urdd Peace Message
OL,6,FShatw Ali, one of the young women who
OL,7,Fcontributed to the message, said:
OL,8,F"Peace is a place where parents don't
OL,9,Fhave to worry about how to feed their
OL,10,Fchildren, where children can watch
OL,11,Ffireworks instead of watching bombs
OL,12,Ffall from the sky.
OL,14,F"It might seem impossible to find a
OL,15,Fplace like that on this planet but if
OL,16,Fyou look carefully, you'll find it,
OL,17,Fjust like how I found Wales. A land,
OL,18,Fan oasis of serenity amidst the
OL,19,Fchaotic world."
